The paper deals with the analysis of error probability in millimeter wave (mmWave) cellular networks, which is a topic related to information theory (cs.IT), network infrastructure (cs.NI), communication systems (cs.COMM), and systems and control (cs.SY). Additionally, the use of stochastic geometry tools suggests that the paper may also be relevant to the field of applied mathematics (cs.MA).
